trans-unit.source: Represents the values that control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 表示控制中的自动完成功能的行为的值<xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox"></xref>控件。

trans-unit.source: To assist with data entry, Internet Explorer 5 and later and some other browsers support a feature named AutoComplete.
trans-unit.target: 若要帮助进行数据输入，Internet Explorer 5 和更高版本以及某些其他浏览器支持一个名为记忆式键入功能。

trans-unit.source: AutoComplete monitors a text box and stores a list of the values that the user has entered.
trans-unit.target: 记忆式键入功能监视文本框中，并将存储的用户输入的值列表。

trans-unit.source: When the user returns to the text box another time, the list of values is displayed.
trans-unit.target: 当用户返回到文本中另一个时间，值的列表。

trans-unit.source: Instead of retyping a value, the user can simply select the value from this list.
trans-unit.target: 而不是重新键入一个值，用户可以只需从此列表中选择值。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Not all browsers support the AutoComplete feature.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE]&1;> 并非所有浏览器都支持记忆式键入功能。

trans-unit.source: Check with your browser to determine compatibility.
trans-unit.target: 请与你的浏览器来确定兼容性。

trans-unit.source: To control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> control, you use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要控制的记忆式键入功能行为<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>控件时，使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A>属性。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: The AutoCompleteType enumeration is used to represent the values that you can apply to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: AutoCompleteType 枚举用于表示的值，可以将应用于<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A>属性。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A>

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A> property for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> control is set to `AutoCompleteType.None`.
trans-unit.target: 默认情况下，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A>属性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>控件设置为`AutoCompleteType.None`。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox.AutoCompleteType%2A>

trans-unit.source: With this setting, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> control shares the list with other <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> controls with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> across different pages.
trans-unit.target: 使用此设置，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>控件与其他共享列表<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>控制具有相同<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>跨不同的页。</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: You can also share a list among <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> controls based on a category instead of based on an <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 你还可以共享之间<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>控件基于类别而不是基于<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>列表

trans-unit.source: When you set the AutoCompleteType property to one of the category values (such as `AutoCompleteType.FirstName` or `AutoCompleteType.LastName`), all <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> controls with the same category share the same list.
trans-unit.target: 当为类别值之一设置 AutoCompleteType 属性 (如`AutoCompleteType.FirstName`或`AutoCompleteType.LastName`)，则所有<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>具有相同类别的控件共享相同的列表。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: You can disable the AutoComplete feature for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox> control by setting the AutoCompleteType property to `AutoCompleteType.Disabled`.
trans-unit.target: 你可以禁用自动完成功能<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>AutoCompleteType 属性设置为控件`AutoCompleteType.Disabled`。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: Refer to your browser documentation for details on configuring and enabling the AutoComplete feature.
trans-unit.target: 请参阅浏览器文档有关配置和启用记忆式键入功能的详细信息。

trans-unit.source: For example, to enable the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer version 5 or later, from the **Tools** menu, choose **Internet Options**.
trans-unit.target: 例如，若要启用 Internet Explorer 5 或更高版本，从版本中的自动完成功能**工具**菜单上，选择**Internet 选项**。

trans-unit.source: Then choose the **Content** tab.
Choose the **AutoComplete** button to view and modify options for the AutoComplete feature.
trans-unit.target: 选择**记忆式键入功能**按钮可查看并修改记忆式键入功能的选项。

trans-unit.source: For more information on the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer, search for [Using AutoComplete in HTML Forms](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/workshop/author/forms/autocomplete_ovr.asp) in the MSDN Library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
trans-unit.target: 有关 Internet Explorer 中的自动完成功能的详细信息，搜索[HTML 窗体中使用自动完成](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/workshop/author/forms/autocomplete_ovr.asp)http://msdn.microsoft.com/library 上 MSDN 库中。
